item.title: Worldofobjets.cfg not found?
item.dc:creator: @metalfan231 metalfan231
item.description:
@metalfan231 wrote:

Yeah. Sometimes if cfg files are removed (like shops, at least on Devolution), nothing happens.
Btw, the easiest way to get that file back is to re download the server. If you edited things, open those files. Then when the server is re downloaded, save them.
